Brent Leland            04/06/2006                                             Added run cycle parameter for new table field 
                                                                                                LAST_UPDT_RUN_CYC_NO
Ralph Tucker          11/02/2006                                             Added PCA_TYP_CD; Direct Map
Brent Leland            04/01/2008                                             Added three additional parralle update SQL.           devlIDS                                   Steph Goddard            04/01/2008




































